title: Bobby's First Interview With Kenny Rogers + 'Songs That Give You Chills' Draft + Matt Jones Went To Dinner With Bobby And His Girlfriend
itunes:title: Bobby's First Interview With Kenny Rogers + 'Songs That Give You Chills' Draft + Matt Jones Went To Dinner With Bobby And His Girlfriend
description:
Kenny Rogers passed away over the weekend at the age of 81. Bobby shared the interview from the first time we met Kenny back in 2013. We looked back on his career and his relationship with Dolly Parton. We also draft the songs that give you chills. Plus, we talk to Matt Jones from Kentucky Sports Radio about meeting Bobby for the first time and having dinner with him and his girlfriend.
